      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question... im on sertraline for my depression but it doesnt feel like it's doing much lately since finals are starting and im super stressed. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost my mood naturally, is that cool to take them together? or is there any reason i shouldn't?",
