      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait r u sure? i read online that because st johns wort is just a plant/natural it's usually fine to mix with meds. like, it's not some heavy chemical drug, so the risk of it being \"dangerous\" seems kind of exaggerated right? i just really need something to help me get through these next two weeks of exams.",
